caption: A young woman in knee-high rubber boots and a black long-sleeve shirt with an athletic logo stands in a grassy field, holding a rope in her left hand that is tied to a horse's green bit, on her right. The horse faces toward a firepit in the foreground, along with the woman. In the background, an older white male with a baseball cap, blue shirt, blue jeans, and a lanyard looks toward the fire as well. A horse walks partially off camera to his left. There are logs scattered on the background behind the man and the second horse. Wooden fences are in the far background, and a forest is behind them.
